{
  "video_id": "FrxDrpi1XNU",
  "title": "Christopher Soghoian: Government surveillance — this is just the beginning",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12811.0,
      "end_time": 14776.0,
      "text": "The 2011 Arab Spring"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14776.0,
      "end_time": 16579.0,
      "text": "captured the attention of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16579.0,
      "end_time": 18228.0,
      "text": "It also captured the attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18228.0,
      "end_time": 20605.0,
      "text": "of authoritarian governments in other countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20605.0,
      "end_time": 23568.0,
      "text": "who were worried that revolution would spread."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23568.0,
      "end_time": 25645.0,
      "text": "To respond, they ramped up surveillance"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25645.0,
      "end_time": 28741.0,
      "text": "of activists, journalists and dissidents"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28741.0,
      "end_time": 30695.0,
      "text": "who they feared would inspire revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30695.0,
      "end_time": 32530.0,
      "text": "in their own countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32530.0,
      "end_time": 34575.0,
      "text": "One prominent Bahraini activist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34575.0,
      "end_time": 36685.0,
      "text": "who was arrested and tortured by his government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36685.0,
      "end_time": 38410.0,
      "text": "has said that the interrogators showed him"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38410.0,
      "end_time": 40279.0,
      "text": "transcripts of his telephone calls"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40280.0,
      "end_time": 42880.0,
      "text": "and text messages."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 42880.0,
      "end_time": 43744.0,
      "text": "Of course, it&#39;s no secret"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43744.0,
      "end_time": 46940.0,
      "text": "that governments are able to intercept telephone calls and text messages."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46940.0,
      "end_time": 49312.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s for that reason that many activists"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49312.0,
      "end_time": 51238.0,
      "text": "specifically avoid using the telephone."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51238.0,
      "end_time": 53586.0,
      "text": "Instead, they use tools like Skype,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 53586.0,
      "end_time": 56106.0,
      "text": "which they think are immune to interception."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56106.0,
      "end_time": 57878.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 57878.0,
      "end_time": 60604.0,
      "text": "There have now been over the last few years"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 60604.0,
      "end_time": 62250.0,
      "text": "an industry of companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 62250.0,
      "end_time": 65504.0,
      "text": "who provide surveillance technology to governments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 65504.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67865.0,
      "text": "specifically technology that allows those governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 67865.0,
      "end_time": 69518.0,
      "text": "to hack into the computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 69518.0,
      "end_time": 71113.0,
      "text": "of surveillance targets."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 71113.0,
      "end_time": 73953.0,
      "text": "Rather than intercepting the communications  as they go over the wire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 73953.0,
      "end_time": 76220.0,
      "text": "instead they now hack into your computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 76220.0,
      "end_time": 78222.0,
      "text": "enable your webcam, enable your microphone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 78222.0,
      "end_time": 80678.0,
      "text": "and steal documents from your computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 80679.0,
      "end_time": 83512.0,
      "text": "When the government of Egypt fell in 2011,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 83512.0,
      "end_time": 86913.0,
      "text": "activists raided the office of the secret police,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 86913.0,
      "end_time": 88901.0,
      "text": "and among the many documents they found"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 88901.0,
      "end_time": 91217.0,
      "text": "was this document by the Gamma Corporation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 91218.0,
      "end_time": 93190.0,
      "text": "by Gamma International."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 93190.0,
      "end_time": 94676.0,
      "text": "Gamma is a German company"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 94676.0,
      "end_time": 96160.0,
      "text": "that manufactures surveillance software"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 96160.0,
      "end_time": 98317.0,
      "text": "and sells it only to governments."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 98317.0,
      "end_time": 100324.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s important to note that most governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 100324.0,
      "end_time": 102390.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t really have the in-house capabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 102390.0,
      "end_time": 103855.0,
      "text": "to develop this software."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 103855.0,
      "end_time": 105474.0,
      "text": "Smaller ones don&#39;t have the resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 105474.0,
      "end_time": 107250.0,
      "text": "or the expertise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 107250.0,
      "end_time": 110557.0,
      "text": "and so there&#39;s this market of Western companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 110557.0,
      "end_time": 112524.0,
      "text": "who are happy to supply them with the tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 112524.0,
      "end_time": 114242.0,
      "text": "and techniques for a price."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 114242.0,
      "end_time": 116848.0,
      "text": "Gamma is just one of these companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 116848.0,
      "end_time": 119756.0,
      "text": "I should note also that Gamma never actually sold"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 119756.0,
      "end_time": 121653.0,
      "text": "their software to the Egyptian government."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 121653.0,
      "end_time": 124250.0,
      "text": "They&#39;d sent them an invoice for a sale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 124250.0,
      "end_time": 125892.0,
      "text": "but the Egyptians never bought it."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 125892.0,
      "end_time": 127616.0,
      "text": "Instead, apparently, the Egyptian government"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 127616.0,
      "end_time": 130249.0,
      "text": "used a free demo version of Gamma&#39;s software."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 130249.0,
      "end_time": 133240.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 133240.0,
      "end_time": 136522.0,
      "text": "So this screenshot is from a sales video"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 136522.0,
      "end_time": 138870.0,
      "text": "that Gamma produced."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 138870.0,
      "end_time": 140700.0,
      "text": "Really, they&#39;re just emphasizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 140700.0,
      "end_time": 141721.0,
      "text": "in a relatively slick presentation"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 141721.0,
      "end_time": 143914.0,
      "text": "the fact that the police can sort of sit"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 143914.0,
      "end_time": 145363.0,
      "text": "in an air-conditioned office"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 145364.0,
      "end_time": 146775.0,
      "text": "and remotely monitor someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 146775.0,
      "end_time": 148950.0,
      "text": "without them having any idea that it&#39;s going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 148950.0,
      "end_time": 150984.0,
      "text": "You know, your webcam light won&#39;t turn on."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 150985.0,
      "end_time": 154339.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s nothing to indicate that the microphone is enabled."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 154339.0,
      "end_time": 157674.0,
      "text": "This is the managing director of Gamma International."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 157674.0,
      "end_time": 159535.0,
      "text": "His name is Martin Muench."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 159535.0,
      "end_time": 162466.0,
      "text": "There are many photos of Mr. Muench that exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 162466.0,
      "end_time": 164318.0,
      "text": "This is perhaps my favorite."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 164318.0,
      "end_time": 166462.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m just going to zoom in a little bit onto his webcam."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 166462.0,
      "end_time": 168130.0,
      "text": "You can see there&#39;s a little sticker"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 168130.0,
      "end_time": 170230.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s placed over his camera."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 170230.0,
      "end_time": 172555.0,
      "text": "He knows what kind of surveillance is possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 172556.0,
      "end_time": 174362.0,
      "text": "and so clearly he doesn&#39;t want it to be used"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 174362.0,
      "end_time": 175964.0,
      "text": "against him."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 175964.0,
      "end_time": 177888.0,
      "text": "Muench has said that he intends"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 177888.0,
      "end_time": 179552.0,
      "text": "for his software to be used"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 179552.0,
      "end_time": 182535.0,
      "text": "to capture terrorists and locate pedophiles."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 182535.0,
      "end_time": 184331.0,
      "text": "Of course, he&#39;s also acknowledged that once"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 184331.0,
      "end_time": 186486.0,
      "text": "the software has been sold to governments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 186486.0,
      "end_time": 190310.0,
      "text": "he has no way of knowing how it can be used."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 190311.0,
      "end_time": 192161.0,
      "text": "Gamma&#39;s software has been located on servers"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 192161.0,
      "end_time": 193817.0,
      "text": "in countries around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 193817.0,
      "end_time": 196208.0,
      "text": "many with really atrocious track records"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 196208.0,
      "end_time": 197769.0,
      "text": "and human rights violations."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 197769.0,
      "end_time": 201164.0,
      "text": "They really are selling their software around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 201164.0,
      "end_time": 203464.0,
      "text": "Gamma is not the only company in the business."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 203465.0,
      "end_time": 206216.0,
      "text": "As I said, it&#39;s a $5 billion industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 206216.0,
      "end_time": 209550.0,
      "text": "One of the other big guys in the industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 209550.0,
      "end_time": 211450.0,
      "text": "is an Italian company called Hacking Team."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 211450.0,
      "end_time": 213174.0,
      "text": "Now, Hacking Team has what is probably"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 213175.0,
      "end_time": 215145.0,
      "text": "the slickest presentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 215145.0,
      "end_time": 218173.0,
      "text": "The video they&#39;ve produced is very sexy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 218173.0,
      "end_time": 219821.0,
      "text": "and so I&#39;m going to play you a clip"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 219821.0,
      "end_time": 221135.0,
      "text": "just so you can get a feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 221135.0,
      "end_time": 222965.0,
      "text": "both for the capabilities of the software"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 222966.0,
      "end_time": 224872.0,
      "text": "but also how it&#39;s marketed"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 224872.0,
      "end_time": 226640.0,
      "text": "to their government clients."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 226640.0,
      "end_time": 230155.0,
      "text": "(Video) Narrator: You want to look  through your target&#39;s eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 230179.0,
      "end_time": 232630.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 232630.0,
      "end_time": 235650.0,
      "text": "You have to hack your target."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 235650.0,
      "end_time": 241381.0,
      "text": "[\"While your target is browsing the web, exchanging documents, receiving SMS, crossing the borders\"]"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 241381.0,
      "end_time": 244304.0,
      "text": "You have to hit many different platforms."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 244304.0,
      "end_time": 248184.0,
      "text": "[\"Windows, OS X, iOS, Android, Blackberry, Symbian, Linux\"]"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 248184.0,
      "end_time": 250652.0,
      "text": "You have to overcome encryption"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 250652.0,
      "end_time": 253548.0,
      "text": "and capture relevant data."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 253549.0,
      "end_time": 258108.0,
      "text": "[Skype & encrypted calls, target location,  messaging, relationships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 258108.0,
      "end_time": 261280.0,
      "text": "web browsing, audio & video\"]"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 261279.0,
      "end_time": 265440.0,
      "text": "Being stealth and untraceable."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 265440.0,
      "end_time": 268714.0,
      "text": "[\"Immune to any protection system Hidden collection infrastructure\"]"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 268714.0,
      "end_time": 272819.0,
      "text": "Deployed all over your country."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 272819.0,
      "end_time": 277353.0,
      "text": "[\"Up to hundreds of thousands of targets Managed from a single spot\"]"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 277353.0,
      "end_time": 280675.0,
      "text": "Exactly what we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 280675.0,
      "end_time": 282938.0,
      "text": "Christopher Soghoian: So, it would be funny if it wasn&#39;t true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 282938.0,
      "end_time": 284726.0,
      "text": "but, in fact, Hacking Team&#39;s software"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 284726.0,
      "end_time": 287674.0,
      "text": "is being sold to governments around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 287674.0,
      "end_time": 289426.0,
      "text": "Last year we learned, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 289426.0,
      "end_time": 293474.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s been used to target Moroccan  journalists by the Moroccan government."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 293474.0,
      "end_time": 296180.0,
      "text": "Many, many countries it&#39;s been found in."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 296180.0,
      "end_time": 299142.0,
      "text": "So, Hacking Team has also been actively courting"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 299142.0,
      "end_time": 301485.0,
      "text": "the U.S. law enforcement market."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 301485.0,
      "end_time": 303768.0,
      "text": "In the last year or so, the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 303768.0,
      "end_time": 308544.0,
      "text": "has opened a sales office in Maryland."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 308544.0,
      "end_time": 310657.0,
      "text": "The company has also hired a spokesperson."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 310658.0,
      "end_time": 312195.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been attending"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 312195.0,
      "end_time": 313792.0,
      "text": "surveillance industry conferences"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 313792.0,
      "end_time": 315806.0,
      "text": "where law enforcement officials show up."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 315807.0,
      "end_time": 317641.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve spoken at the conferences."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 317641.0,
      "end_time": 319229.0,
      "text": "What I thought was most fascinating was"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 319229.0,
      "end_time": 321330.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve actually paid for the coffee break"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 321330.0,
      "end_time": 323270.0,
      "text": "at one of the law enforcement conferences"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 323270.0,
      "end_time": 324763.0,
      "text": "earlier this year."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 324763.0,
      "end_time": 326861.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t tell you for sure that Hacking Team"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 326862.0,
      "end_time": 329587.0,
      "text": "has sold their technology in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 329587.0,
      "end_time": 331558.0,
      "text": "but what I can tell you that if they haven&#39;t sold it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 331558.0,
      "end_time": 334733.0,
      "text": "it isn&#39;t because they haven&#39;t been trying hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 334733.0,
      "end_time": 336775.0,
      "text": "So as I said before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 336775.0,
      "end_time": 338695.0,
      "text": "governments that don&#39;t really have the resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 338695.0,
      "end_time": 340291.0,
      "text": "to build their own tools will buy"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 340291.0,
      "end_time": 341701.0,
      "text": "off-the-shelf surveillance software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 341701.0,
      "end_time": 343890.0,
      "text": "and so for that reason,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 343890.0,
      "end_time": 345805.0,
      "text": "you see that the government of, say, Tunisia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 345805.0,
      "end_time": 347993.0,
      "text": "might use the same software as the government of Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 347993.0,
      "end_time": 350265.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re all buying off-the-shelf stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 350265.0,
      "end_time": 352464.0,
      "text": "The Federal Bureau of Investigation in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 352464.0,
      "end_time": 355226.0,
      "text": "does have the budget to build their own surveillance technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 355226.0,
      "end_time": 357700.0,
      "text": "and so for several years, I&#39;ve been trying"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 357700.0,
      "end_time": 359398.0,
      "text": "to figure out if and how the FBI"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 359398.0,
      "end_time": 362296.0,
      "text": "is hacking into the computers of surveillance targets."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 362296.0,
      "end_time": 365449.0,
      "text": "My friends at an organization called the Electronic Frontier Foundation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 365449.0,
      "end_time": 367761.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re a civil society group —"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 367761.0,
      "end_time": 370253.0,
      "text": "obtained hundreds of documents from the FBI"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 370253.0,
      "end_time": 373101.0,
      "text": "detailing their next generation of surveillance technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 373101.0,
      "end_time": 375735.0,
      "text": "Most of these documents were heavily redacted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 375735.0,
      "end_time": 378551.0,
      "text": "but what you can see from the slides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 378551.0,
      "end_time": 380513.0,
      "text": "if I zoom in, is this term:"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 380513.0,
      "end_time": 382332.0,
      "text": "Remote Operations Unit."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 382333.0,
      "end_time": 384567.0,
      "text": "Now, when I first looked into this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 384567.0,
      "end_time": 386637.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d never heard of this unit before."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 386637.0,
      "end_time": 388939.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been studying surveillance for more than six years."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 388939.0,
      "end_time": 390224.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d never heard of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 390224.0,
      "end_time": 392187.0,
      "text": "And so I went online and I did some research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 392187.0,
      "end_time": 394312.0,
      "text": "and ultimately I hit the mother lode"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 394312.0,
      "end_time": 395946.0,
      "text": "when I went to LinkedIn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 395946.0,
      "end_time": 398515.0,
      "text": "the social networking site for job seekers."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 398515.0,
      "end_time": 401428.0,
      "text": "There were lots of former U.S. government contractors"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 401428.0,
      "end_time": 402815.0,
      "text": "who had at one point worked"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 402815.0,
      "end_time": 404124.0,
      "text": "for the Remote Operating Unit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 404124.0,
      "end_time": 407538.0,
      "text": "and were describing in surprising detail on their CVs"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 407538.0,
      "end_time": 409569.0,
      "text": "what they had done in their former job."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 409569.0,
      "end_time": 411791.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 411791.0,
      "end_time": 413778.0,
      "text": "So I took this information"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 413778.0,
      "end_time": 417522.0,
      "text": "and I gave it to a journalist that I know and trust at the Wall Street Journal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 417522.0,
      "end_time": 419323.0,
      "text": "and she was able to contact several other"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 419323.0,
      "end_time": 421770.0,
      "text": "former law enforcement officials"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 421770.0,
      "end_time": 422883.0,
      "text": "who spoke on background and confirmed"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 422883.0,
      "end_time": 426241.0,
      "text": "that yes, in fact, the FBI has a dedicated team"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 426242.0,
      "end_time": 428378.0,
      "text": "that does nothing but hack into the computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 428378.0,
      "end_time": 429904.0,
      "text": "of surveillance targets."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 429904.0,
      "end_time": 431792.0,
      "text": "Like Gamma and Hacking Team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 431792.0,
      "end_time": 433909.0,
      "text": "the FBI also has the capability"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 433909.0,
      "end_time": 437303.0,
      "text": "to remotely activate webcams, microphones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 437303.0,
      "end_time": 439505.0,
      "text": "steal documents, get web browsing information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 439505.0,
      "end_time": 441189.0,
      "text": "the works."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 441189.0,
      "end_time": 443110.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s sort of a big problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 443110.0,
      "end_time": 444611.0,
      "text": "with governments going into hacking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 444611.0,
      "end_time": 447130.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s that terrorists, pedophiles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 447130.0,
      "end_time": 450410.0,
      "text": "drug dealers, journalists and human rights activists"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 450410.0,
      "end_time": 452312.0,
      "text": "all use the same kinds of computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 452312.0,
      "end_time": 454359.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no drug dealer phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 454359.0,
      "end_time": 456325.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s no journalist laptop."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 456325.0,
      "end_time": 458558.0,
      "text": "We all use the same technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 458559.0,
      "end_time": 460453.0,
      "text": "and what that means then is that for governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 460453.0,
      "end_time": 462570.0,
      "text": "to have the capability to hack into the computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 462570.0,
      "end_time": 464269.0,
      "text": "of the real bad guys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 464269.0,
      "end_time": 466245.0,
      "text": "they also have to have the capability"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 466245.0,
      "end_time": 468430.0,
      "text": "to hack into our devices too."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 468430.0,
      "end_time": 470182.0,
      "text": "So governments around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 470182.0,
      "end_time": 471643.0,
      "text": "have been embracing this technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 471643.0,
      "end_time": 473248.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been embracing hacking"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 473248.0,
      "end_time": 475680.0,
      "text": "as a law enforcement technique,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 475680.0,
      "end_time": 477180.0,
      "text": "but without any real debate."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 477180.0,
      "end_time": 478837.0,
      "text": "In the United States, where I live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 478837.0,
      "end_time": 480662.0,
      "text": "there have been no congressional hearings."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 480662.0,
      "end_time": 482623.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no law that&#39;s been passed"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 482623.0,
      "end_time": 484695.0,
      "text": "specifically authorizing this technique,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 484696.0,
      "end_time": 487365.0,
      "text": "and because of its power and potential for abuse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 487365.0,
      "end_time": 490312.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s vital that we have an informed public debate."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 490312.0,
      "end_time": 492258.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 492258.0,
      "end_time": 493813.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}